# Cosmic Nova: A Madlibs Game Project

## Introduction

Welcome to Cosmic Nova, a cool Madlibs game that takes you on an interstellar word adventure!  have fun filling in the blanks to create galagtic giggles stories on Cosmic Nova planet.

> "Ad Astra Per Aspera" - To the stars through difficulties.

